==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Headnote
<hw>Head"note`</hw> <pr>(-n⟦omac⟧t`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A note at
the head of a page or chapter; in law reports, an abstract of a case,
showing the principles involved and the opinion of the court.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

